OL,3,CFundraiser for library destroyed by
OL,4,Crioters surpasses #250,000
OL,6,FA fundraising campaign has raised more
OL,7,Fthan #250,000 to help repair a library
OL,8,Fand community hub that suffered severe
OL,9,Ffire damage after being targeted by
OL,10,Frioters.
OL,12,FWriter Philip Pullman, children's
OL,13,Flaureate Frank Cottrell-Boyce, and
OL,14,Fchef Nigella Lawson are among those
OL,15,Fwho have donated to the fundraiser,
OL,16,Fwhich was set up in aid of Spellow
OL,17,FLibrary Hub in Walton.
