OL,3,CFundraiser for library destroyed by
OL,4,Crioters surpasses #250,000
OL,6,FThe GoFundMe page had an initial
OL,7,Ftarget of #500 but has gone on to
OL,8,Fraise more than #250,000, from more
OL,9,Fthan 11,000 donations.
OL,11,FThe appeal was started by manicurist
OL,12,FAlex McCormick, 27, who was
OL,13,F"heartbroken" to think that children
OL,14,Fwill miss out on reading in a
OL,15,Fcommunity space which is "meant to be
OL,16,Fsafe."
