OL,3,CFundraiser for library destroyed by
OL,4,Crioters surpasses #250,000
OL,6,FShe said on Tuesday, 20 August, Metro
OL,7,FMayor Steve Rotheram made a "generous
OL,8,Fdonation" of #500 which has pushed the
OL,9,Ftotal to just over a quarter of a
OL,10,Fmillion pounds.
OL,12,FAlex added that the fundraiser has now
OL,13,Fbeen paused as the money is
OL,14,Ftransferred over to Liverpool City
OL,15,FCouncil.
OL,17,FAround 300 people were involved in
OL,18,Fviolent disorder on Saturday, 3
OL,19,FAugust, following the murder of three
OL,20,Fgirls in Southport, Merseyside Police.
