OL,3,CFundraiser for library destroyed by
OL,4,Crioters surpasses #250,000
OL,6,FLooters targeted local businesses, and
OL,7,Fbins were used to start fires before
OL,8,Fthe Spellow Hub Library was set alight.
OL,10,FWhen firefighters arrived at the site
OL,11,Fon County Road, the rioters attempted
OL,12,Fto stop them from getting to the fire
OL,13,Fto put it out.
OL,15,FThe library, which was opened in 2023
OL,16,Fto provide support for one of the most
OL,17,Fdeprived communities in the country,
OL,18,Fsuffered severe damage to the ground
OL,19,Ffloor.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
