OL,3,CFundraiser for library destroyed by
OL,4,Crioters surpasses #250,000
OL,6,FQueen Camilla expressed her sorrow at
OL,7,Fthe recent violent disorder in the
OL,8,Fregion, particularly the attack on the
OL,9,FSpellow Library Hub, and donated a box
OL,10,Fof nearly 70 books.
OL,12,FPride and Prejudice, Swallows and
OL,13,FAmazons and War Horse were among the
OL,14,Fnovels given to the library by Her
OL,15,FMajesty the Queen who has long been a
OL,16,Fchampion of literature.
