OL,3,CFundraiser for library destroyed by
OL,4,Crioters surpasses #250,000
OL,6,FShortly after her donation, Metro
OL,7,FMayor Steve Rotheram said: "The
OL,8,Fburning of a library was such a
OL,9,Fshocking image, symbolising the
OL,10,Fignorance of those who seek to divide
OL,11,Fus.
OL,13,F"With the help of the Queen's
OL,14,Fdonation, and of everyone else who has
OL,15,Fgiven their support, we will ensure
OL,16,Fthat they do not succeed."
OL,18,FMeanwhile, two brothers who looted the
OL,19,Fcommunity hub and library after it was
OL,20,Fset alight have been jailed for their
OL,21,Fpart in the disorder.
